<div class="row w-100 m-0" style="overflow: hidden">
	<div id="section-main" class="sermons-col-left bg-grey" style="width:100%">
		<h1 class="color-1a8090 bg-white text-center pb-2 pt-3 h2">第85屆 講道會 第9講</h1>
		<article class="article pt-0 p-lg-5 pt-lg-0">
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-user"></i>
					講員：					<a href="/speaker/view/36">區伯平牧師</a>
				</span>
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>
					屆別:					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=85">第85屆</a>
				</span>
				<span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="性質">
					<i class="fa fa-folder-open"></i>
					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=85#session-master-48">講道會</a>
				</span>
			</div>
			<!--<div class="article-tag">
				<a href="#" class="badge">路加福音</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">講道會</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">56屆</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">麥希真牧師</a>
			</div>-->
			<div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
				<h2 class="article-title mb-0 h3">
					第九講  生命迷宮怎續航				</h2>
									<a type="button" class="bookmark ms-3 " data-model="app\models\SessionMessage" data-model-id="845"></a>
							</div>
						<div class="article-content">
				
				<div class="h5 mb-4 d-md-flex justify-content-lg-between align-items-center">
					<div><span>經文：</span> 創世記  <a class="article-citation" href="javascript:void(0)" data-book="1" data-start-chapter="17" data-start-verse="1" data-end-verse="8">17:1-8</a></div><div><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="btn btn-danger btn-show-scripture text-center my-2 ml-auto align-self-start" style="display:none;">顯示經文</a>
				</div></div>				<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">99歲的亞伯蘭，開展人生下半場，他即將是百歳老人，在人生的某些關口，需重新立志，再聚焦於上帝，依靠上帝的導航系統，走出生命的迷宮。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">夏甲的兒子已經</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">13歲了，撒萊仍未生子，上帝應許仍然未到，轉眼過了24年，在八千七百多個日子裡，亞伯蘭都活在上帝未成就的應許之下。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">第</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">17章全是上帝對他說話，上帝開宗明義，突顯自己全能的屬性，不是有甚麼難處，以致多年不能成就應許。上帝囑咐亞伯蘭重新立志，活在上帝面前，要作完全人。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">完全，不單指道德。而是要對信仰貫徹始終，堅持到底，完全一生對上帝的信靠。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">對上帝發出的邀請和要求，亞伯蘭五體投地，用身體語言接受上帝的呼籲，立志一生敬畏上帝。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">上帝俯就人的卑微，與亞伯蘭立約，亞伯蘭的靈命再進深一步，將生命再定焦在上帝身上。他改用新的隨身標記：</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">1）改名為亞伯拉罕；2）行割禮。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">亞伯拉罕名字的出現，揭開了開啟人類的新篇章。舊名「亞伯蘭」的意思是：崇高的父。新名「亞伯拉罕」是：多國之父。上帝本是人類之父，衪賜給亞伯拉罕為父的身份和地位，亦是賜給人類一個新的里程碑，叫我們因信稱義，他成為信心之父，我們成為信心的后裔。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">上帝在應許之上又加上標記，這保證是何等肯定！立約，從上帝的宣告開始，並以衪的全能作保證。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">我們守約信靠上帝，有時以為這是冒險，但上帝更冒險，衪為我們押上神聖的聲譽和大能的保證！</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">上帝賜恩給沒有能力的人，我們很難理解。惟有信；信，就是承認人的不明白和不能，就是信上帝的全能，信衪能人所不能</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">...人要超越自己，就該相信超越的上帝。敬畏上帝是走出迷宮唯一出路，因衪在高天之上，引導我們。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">回顧亞伯蘭</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">24年的成敗得失，信上帝也會有不少問題？但若沒有上帝，情況更悽慘。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">從亞伯蘭到亞伯拉罕，九堂課的重點如下：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">1）生兒育女人間世 - 人生可戀，珍惜生命。<br />
2）生離死別活下去 - 仰望上帝，定準人生方向。<br />
3）生活奮鬥新機遇 - 生命突破，在於接受上帝的呼喚。<br />
4）生存逆境亂陣腳 - 偏離上帝，人生更無價值。<br />
5）生疏親情落寞心 - 清心仰望上帝，得最好慰藉，承受大祝福。<br />
6）生財有道適取捨 - 有財不一定有神，但有神就有一切。<br />
7）生機無奈求其次 - 信耶穌是主，任何環境不靠自己，只靠上帝。<br />
8）生不逢時誰之過 - 不靠自己聰明，依靠全智的上帝。<br />
9）生命迷宮怎續航 -數算主恩，重新歸向神。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">我且作一個導遊，帶大家進去聖經花園，看一個個活生生的人物故事，歷世歷代都有艱難，不是你才有。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">聖經是神的話，不是「神話」，上帝以活潑的話，向我們發出生命呼喚和邀請：要作完全人！</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">我們要學習亞伯拉罕</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"> -- 生命要走向成熟，而非僅是世故。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

